title: Lou Dobbs, "The Trump Century: How Our President Changed the Course of History Forever"
description:
Fox Business News host Lou Dobbs offers his thoughts on President Trump’s agenda and America’s future. He’s interviewed by Victor Davis Hanson, author and Hoover Institution senior fellow.
